      "text": [
        " أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"اَلْعَبْدُ اَلْآبِقُ لاَ تُقْبَلُ لَهُ صَلاَةٌ حَتَّى يَرْجِعَ إِلَى مَوْلاَهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3534 - Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), said:\n\"The runaway slave's prayer is not accepted until he returns to his master.\""
        ]
      }
